Perfect! Now I understand the v4 hazards exactly:

1. **`module_cascade_failure`**: triggers when modules ≥ 4, adds `severity_per_module * (total_modules - min_modules)` to systemic damage
2. **`power_grid_overload`**: triggers when modules ≥ 5, drains `power_drain_per_module * (total_modules - min_modules)` power 
3. **`dust_infiltration`**: affects ALL modules, applies `degradation_per_module * total_modules` degradation
4. **`supply_chain_bottleneck`**: triggers when crew ≥ 3 and modules ≥ 3, applies efficiency penalty

